1242
01:33:12,720 --> 01:33:15,000
Because I'm afraid.

1243
01:33:15,040 --> 01:33:18,200
I'm really afraid to be away from here.

1244
01:33:18,240 --> 01:33:22,160
You know, I think, I always knew
I wouldn't go in the end.

1245
01:33:22,640 --> 01:33:24,800
