are you going back with Rachel?

1248
01:33:32,720 --> 01:33:34,640
I don't know.

1249
01:33:34,800 --> 01:33:36,480
I hope so.

1250
01:33:36,960 --> 01:33:38,520
I hope so too.

1251
01:33:38,560 --> 01:33:41,400
Then maybe you'll come back here.

1252
01:33:42,520 --> 01:33:46,080
No, Joel, I'm not coming back.

1253
01:33:49,840 --> 01:33:52,640
I'm through playing basketball.

1254
01:33:55,120 --> 01:33:57,200
You hear that, guys?

1255
01:33:57,400 --> 01:33:59,920
That's it. You can relax.

1256
01:34:08,280 --> 01:34:10,480
You know, these guys.

1257
01:34:11,360 --> 01:34:13,520
They aren't just your dream.

1258
01:34:14,800 --> 01:34:16,800
They were mine too.

1259
01:34:31,880 --> 01:34:34,920
Will you send me
basketball magazines?

1260
01:34:37,040 --> 01:34:39,680
I'll send you any damn thing you want.

